(/rent-vs-buy-calculator)\n-   [How to get pre-approved](/guides/mortgage-pre-approval)\n\n[Real Estate Agents ▾](/real-estate-agents)\n\n-   [Find an Agent](/real-estate-agents)\n-   [Join as a Redfin Agent](https://careers.redfin.com/real-estate)\n-   [Join our referral network](/partners)\n-   [Agent Resource Center](/guides/agent-resources)\n\n[Feed](/feed \"Feed\")\n\nJoin / Sign in\n\n![](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/homepage/homepage-hero-neighborhood-homes.jpg)\n\n# Redfin Early Access.  \nFind it first.\n\n-   Buy\n-   Mortgage\n-   Sell\n-   Rent\n-   My Home Value\n\n![alt](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/hpwidget/RedfinAgentNew.png)\n\n[\n\n### Buy\n\n](/real-estate-agents)\n\nRedfin agents are among the most experienced in the industry and can help you win in today’s market.[](/disclaimer)\n\nFind an agent\n\n![alt](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/hpwidget/HomeFinance.png)\n\n[\n\n### Mortgage\n\n](/mortgage-purchase-or-refinance?context=153)\n\nRocket Mortgage[](/disclaimer) delivers award-winning service with competitive rates, fast pre-approvals, and seamless closings.\n\nGet prequalified\n\n![alt](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/hpwidget/SellNew.png)\n\n[\n\n### Sell\n\n](/why-sell)\n\nWe know how to price, market, and sell your home for top dollar. And we do it all for half the listing fee others often charge.[](/disclaimer)\n\nLearn more\n\n![alt](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/hpwidget/RentNew.png)\n\n[\n\n### Rent\n\n](/rentals)\n\nWhether you’re searching for apartments, condos, or rental homes, we make it easy to find a place you’ll love.\n\nExplore rentals\n\n![Mobile phone with QR code.](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/cop-assets/prod/hpwidget/DownloadApp_DesktopNew.png)\n\n## Get the Redfin app\n\nDownload our top-rated real estate app for iOS or Android to get alerts the moment your dream home hits the market.\n\n## Talk to a Redfin agent\n\nYou’ll be connected with an expert local agent—there’s no pressure or obligation.\n\n### Ask an Agent\n\nWe’re here to help seven days a week.\n\nWhere are you searching for homes?\n\n## Browse the newest homes from around the country\n\n[Chesapeake, VA](/city/4144/VA/Chesapeake/newest-listings)[Grand Rapids, MI](/city/8694/MI/Grand-Rapids/newest-listings)[Jacksonville, FL](/city/8907/FL/Jacksonville/newest-listings)[Jackson, MS](/city/9165/MS/Jackson/newest-listings)[Indianapolis, IN](/city/9170/IN/Indianapolis/newest-listings)[Knoxville, TN](/city/10200/TN/Knoxville/newest-listings)[Norfolk, VA](/city/14757/VA/Norfolk/newest-listings)[Truckee, CA](/city/20216/CA/Truckee/newest-listings)[Virginia Beach, VA](/city/20418/VA/Virginia-Beach/newest-listings)[Kansas City, MO](/city/35751/MO/Kansas-City/newest-listings)\n\nSearch for homes by city\n\n-   [Albuquerque real estate](/city/513/NM/Albuquerque \"Albuquerque real estate\")\n-   [Alexandria real estate](/city/250/VA/Alexandria \"Alexandria real estate\")\n-   [Anchorage real estate](/city/781/AK/Anchorage \"Anchorage real estate\")\n-   [Arlington real estate](/city/21282/VA/Arlington \"Arlington real estate\")\n-   [Ashburn real estate](/city/29015/VA/Ashburn \"Ashburn real estate\")\n-   [Atlanta real estate](/city/30756/GA/Atlanta \"Atlanta real estate\")\n-   [Aurora real estate](/city/29459/IL/Aurora \"Aurora real estate\")\n-   [Austin real estate](/city/30818/TX/Austin \"Austin real estate\")\n-   [Bakersfield real estate](/city/953/CA/Bakersfield \"Bakersfield real estate\")\n-   [Baltimore real estate](/city/1073/MD/Baltimore \"Baltimore real estate\")\n-   [Baton Rouge real estate](/city/1336/LA/Baton-Rouge \"Baton Rouge real estate\")\n-   [Beaverton real estate](/city/1432/OR/Beaverton \"Beaverton real estate\")\n-   [Bend real estate](/city/1543/OR/Bend \"Bend real estate\")\n-   [Birmingham real estate](/city/1823/AL/Birmingham \"Birmingham real estate\")\n-   [Boca Raton real estate](/city/1903/FL/Boca-Raton \"Boca Raton real estate\")\n-   [