5% of the loan amount, up to $6,000. Offer valid only on retail loans with conforming loan limits, and cannot be combined with any other discounts. Rocket Mortgage may cancel/modify this offer at any time. Additional restrictions/conditions apply. This is not a commitment to lend.\n\n[![Download the Redfin App on the Apple App Store](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/vLATEST/images/apple-app-download-badge-284x84.png)](https://redfin.onelink.me/iy7h/wk66abnm)\n\n[![Download the Redfin App from the Google Play Store](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/vLATEST/images/google-app-download-badge-284x84.png)](https://redfin.onelink.me/iy7h/wk66abnm)\n\nJoin us\n\n[Become an Agent](https://careers.redfin.com/real-estate)\n\n[Get referrals](https://www.redfin.com/partners)\n\n[Careers](https://careers.rocket.com/us/en/)\n\nFind homes faster\n\n[![Download the Redfin App on the Apple App Store](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/vLATEST/images/apple-app-download-badge-284x84.png)](https://redfin.onelink.me/iy7h/wk66abnm)\n\n[![Download the Redfin App from the Google Play Store](https://ssl.cdn-redfin.com/vLATEST/images/google-app-download-badge-284x84.png)](https://redfin.onelink.me/iy7h/wk66abnm)\n\nAbout us\n\n[Why Redfin?](/why-redfin)\n\n[Community Impact](https://careers.rocket.com/us/en/culture/community)\n\n[Inclusion](https://careers.rocket.com/us/en/culture/inclusion)\n\n[Culture](https://careers.rocket.com/us/en/culture/philosophies)\n\n[Press](https://www.redfin.com/news/press-center/)\n\n[Investors](https://ir.rocketcompanies.com/)\n\n[Blog](https://www.redfin.com/blog/)\n\n[Real Estate News](https://www.redfin.com/news/)\n\nFind us\n\n[Contact Us](/about/contact-us)\n\n[Help Center](https://support.redfin.com/hc/en-us)\n\nAdvertise\n\n-   [](https://www.facebook.com/redfin \"Redfin Facebook\")\n-   [](https://twitter.com/Redfin \"Redfin Twitter\")\n-   [](https://www.tiktok.com/@redfinrealestate \"Redfin TikTok\")\n-   [](https://www.instagram.com/redfinrealestate/ \"Redfin Instagram\