{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779181945353,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"call_00_8X3naOU0iAUFYVH5YVMq3694","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","oldString":"**Renter Hub (Dashboard):**\n- Sidebar nav: Search, Saved Searches, Favorites, Messages, Applications, Payments\n- Central dashboard showing recent activity, application statuses\n- \"Your search\" section: active searches with new listing counts\n\n---","newString":"**Renter Hub (Dashboard):**\n- Sidebar nav: Search, Saved Searches, Favorites, Messages, Applications, Payments\n- Central dashboard showing recent activity, application statuses\n- \"Your search\" section: active searches with new listing counts\n\n**Mobile Bottom Nav (Zillow homepage):**\n- Search | Updates | Favorites | Home Loans | Inbox\n- 5-tab pattern; Favorites and Updates keep users returning\n\n**Zillow Group Ecosystem (subsidiaries):**\n- Trulia (trulia.com), StreetEasy (streeteasy.com), HotPads (hotpads.com), Out East (outeast.com)\n- All share design DNA (card-based listings, map integration), adapted for regional/demographic needs\n\n---"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n+++ /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n@@ -67,8 +67,16 @@\n - Sidebar nav: Search, Saved Searches, Favorites, Messages, Applications, Payments\n - Central dashboard showing recent activity, application statuses\n - \"Your search\" section: active searches with new listing counts\n \n+**Mobile Bottom Nav (Zillow homepage):**\n+- Search | Updates | Favorites | Home Loans | Inbox\n+- 5-tab pattern; Favorites and Updates keep users returning\n+\n+**Zillow Group Ecosystem (subsidiaries):**\n+- Trulia (trulia.com), StreetEasy (streeteasy.com), HotPads (hotpads.com), Out East (outeast.com)\n+- All share design DNA (card-based listings, map integration), adapted for regional/demographic needs\n+\n ---\n \n ### Competitor 2: Apartments.com\n \n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","patch":"Index: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n+++ /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n@@ -67,8 +67,16 @@\n - Sidebar nav: Search, Saved Searches, Favorites, Messages, Applications, Payments\n - Central dashboard showing recent activity, application statuses\n - \"Your search\" section: active searches with new listing counts\n \n+**Mobile Bottom Nav (Zillow homepage):**\n+- Search | Updates | Favorites | Home Loans | Inbox\n+- 5-tab pattern; Favorites and Updates keep users returning\n+\n+**Zillow Group Ecosystem (subsidiaries):**\n+- Trulia (trulia.com), StreetEasy (streeteasy.com), HotPads (hotpads.com), Out East (outeast.com)\n+- All share design DNA (card-based listings, map integration), adapted for regional/demographic needs\n+\n ---\n \n ### Competitor 2: Apartments.com\n \n","additions":8,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779181945032,"end":1779181945351}},"id":"prt_e3f81dd39001sqCYVBcwFeuBtU","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f81bce2001cDNTynKC0gEj1N"}}
