{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182011607,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"call_00_mDP7yk8NKki8Rtgcr33F4406","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","newString":"### Competitor 4: Rent.com (rent.com)\n\n**Type:** Rental-only marketplace (Redfin subsidiary since 2012)\n**USP:** Focused exclusively on rentals (no sales), strong brand recognition as \"Rent.\"\n\n**Live analysis (2026-05-19):**\n\n**Landing Page Structure:**\n1. **Top Nav** — Logo, Saved (0 badge), List a Property, Business Solutions, Moving Center, Log In, Sign Up\n2. **Hero** — \"Find your perfect place.\" + large search input + trending properties card grid\n3. **\"Properties for you\"** — Grid of trending/featured property cards with: property image (3:2 ratio), price, name/address, bed/bath summary, badges (\"$55 Price Drop\", \"1 Month Free!\", \"Popular\")\n4. **\"Renter tips and insights\"** — Blog card grid with 3 articles: \"11 Steps to Follow When Renting an Apartment\", \"Rent Calculator: How Much Should You Spend on Rent?\", \"The Best US Cities for Hybrid Work\"\n5. **\"Popular Searches\"** — Structured browse directory organized as: Rentals Near Me, Apartments For Rent By City (~50 cities), Houses For Rent By City (~80 cities), Rentals By State (all 50)\n6. **\"The fastest way to rent a home is with the app\"** — Strong mobile app promotion with app store badges, QR code, \"Scan to get the app\"\n7. **Footer** — 4-column: Our Company (Redfin.com, Blog, Research, Legal), Popular Searches (8 categories), Let Us Help (App, Avoid Scams, List Property, Business Solutions, Rent Estimator, Accessibility), App badges\n\n**Property Card Pattern (Rent.com):**\n- Image: ~400x270px, 3:2 ratio\n- Badges on image: \"$55 Price Drop\" (green), \"1 Month Free!\" (blue), \"Popular\" (orange)\n- Below image: Price (large, bold), Property name, Address (street + city/state/ZIP), Bed/Bath (e.g., \"1–2 Beds • 1–2 Baths\")\n- No heart/favorite icon visible on cards (favoriting may require signed-in state)\n\n**Key Insight:** Rent.com uses badges aggressively on property cards to highlight deals and urgency — Price Drop, Month Free, and Popular badges create FOMO and scanability.\n\n**Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n- Property card badges (Price Reduced, New Listing, Popular) increase engagement\n- Blog/resource section establishes authority and improves SEO\n- Browse-by-directory structure (city/state hierarchy) is critical for SEO traffic\n\n---","oldString":"### Competitor 4: Rentable (rentable.co)"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n+++ /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n@@ -176,10 +176,39 @@\n - Trust-building elements: host profiles, reviews, verified badges\n \n ---\n \n-### Competitor 4: Rentable (rentable.co)\n+### Competitor 4: Rent.com (rent.com)\n \n+**Type:** Rental-only marketplace (Redfin subsidiary since 2012)\n+**USP:** Focused exclusively on rentals (no sales), strong brand recognition as \"Rent.\"\n+\n+**Live analysis (2026-05-19):**\n+\n+**Landing Page Structure:**\n+1. **Top Nav** — Logo, Saved (0 badge), List a Property, Business Solutions, Moving Center, Log In, Sign Up\n+2. **Hero** — \"Find your perfect place.\" + large search input + trending properties card grid\n+3. **\"Properties for you\"** — Grid of trending/featured property cards with: property image (3:2 ratio), price, name/address, bed/bath summary, badges (\"$55 Price Drop\", \"1 Month Free!\", \"Popular\")\n+4. **\"Renter tips and insights\"** — Blog card grid with 3 articles: \"11 Steps to Follow When Renting an Apartment\", \"Rent Calculator: How Much Should You Spend on Rent?\", \"The Best US Cities for Hybrid Work\"\n+5. **\"Popular Searches\"** — Structured browse directory organized as: Rentals Near Me, Apartments For Rent By City (~50 cities), Houses For Rent By City (~80 cities), Rentals By State (all 50)\n+6. **\"The fastest way to rent a home is with the app\"** — Strong mobile app promotion with app store badges, QR code, \"Scan to get the app\"\n+7. **Footer** — 4-column: Our Company (Redfin.com, Blog, Research, Legal), Popular Searches (8 categories), Let Us Help (App, Avoid Scams, List Property, Business Solutions, Rent Estimator, Accessibility), App badges\n+\n+**Property Card Pattern (Rent.com):**\n+- Image: ~400x270px, 3:2 ratio\n+- Badges on image: \"$55 Price Drop\" (green), \"1 Month Free!\" (blue), \"Popular\" (orange)\n+- Below image: Price (large, bold), Property name, Address (street + city/state/ZIP), Bed/Bath (e.g., \"1–2 Beds • 1–2 Baths\")\n+- No heart/favorite icon visible on cards (favoriting may require signed-in state)\n+\n+**Key Insight:** Rent.com uses badges aggressively on property cards to highlight deals and urgency — Price Drop, Month Free, and Popular badges create FOMO and scanability.\n+\n+**Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n+- Property card badges (Price Reduced, New Listing, Popular) increase engagement\n+- Blog/resource section establishes authority and improves SEO\n+- Browse-by-directory structure (city/state hierarchy) is critical for SEO traffic\n+\n+---\n+\n **Type:** Rental marketplace with verified listings focus\n **USP:** Human-verified listings, budget calculator, mobile-first\n \n **Landing Page Patterns:**\n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","patch":"Index: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n+++ /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md\n@@ -176,10 +176,39 @@\n - Trust-building elements: host profiles, reviews, verified badges\n \n ---\n \n-### Competitor 4: Rentable (rentable.co)\n+### Competitor 4: Rent.com (rent.com)\n \n+**Type:** Rental-only marketplace (Redfin subsidiary since 2012)\n+**USP:** Focused exclusively on rentals (no sales), strong brand recognition as \"Rent.\"\n+\n+**Live analysis (2026-05-19):**\n+\n+**Landing Page Structure:**\n+1. **Top Nav** — Logo, Saved (0 badge), List a Property, Business Solutions, Moving Center, Log In, Sign Up\n+2. **Hero** — \"Find your perfect place.\" + large search input + trending properties card grid\n+3. **\"Properties for you\"** — Grid of trending/featured property cards with: property image (3:2 ratio), price, name/address, bed/bath summary, badges (\"$55 Price Drop\", \"1 Month Free!\", \"Popular\")\n+4. **\"Renter tips and insights\"** — Blog card grid with 3 articles: \"11 Steps to Follow When Renting an Apartment\", \"Rent Calculator: How Much Should You Spend on Rent?\", \"The Best US Cities for Hybrid Work\"\n+5. **\"Popular Searches\"** — Structured browse directory organized as: Rentals Near Me, Apartments For Rent By City (~50 cities), Houses For Rent By City (~80 cities), Rentals By State (all 50)\n+6. **\"The fastest way to rent a home is with the app\"** — Strong mobile app promotion with app store badges, QR code, \"Scan to get the app\"\n+7. **Footer** — 4-column: Our Company (Redfin.com, Blog, Research, Legal), Popular Searches (8 categories), Let Us Help (App, Avoid Scams, List Property, Business Solutions, Rent Estimator, Accessibility), App badges\n+\n+**Property Card Pattern (Rent.com):**\n+- Image: ~400x270px, 3:2 ratio\n+- Badges on image: \"$55 Price Drop\" (green), \"1 Month Free!\" (blue), \"Popular\" (orange)\n+- Below image: Price (large, bold), Property name, Address (street + city/state/ZIP), Bed/Bath (e.g., \"1–2 Beds • 1–2 Baths\")\n+- No heart/favorite icon visible on cards (favoriting may require signed-in state)\n+\n+**Key Insight:** Rent.com uses badges aggressively on property cards to highlight deals and urgency — Price Drop, Month Free, and Popular badges create FOMO and scanability.\n+\n+**Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n+- Property card badges (Price Reduced, New Listing, Popular) increase engagement\n+- Blog/resource section establishes authority and improves SEO\n+- Browse-by-directory structure (city/state hierarchy) is critical for SEO traffic\n+\n+---\n+\n **Type:** Rental marketplace with verified listings focus\n **USP:** Human-verified listings, budget calculator, mobile-first\n \n **Landing Page Patterns:**\n","additions":30,"deletions":1},"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779182011221,"end":1779182011605}},"id":"prt_e3f82a464001DOMSZr3z60P57A","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f8296ae001T02WYaYZTPt6LD"}}
