{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182020515,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_eQ7X7T0n5Opgl0ckL2Mg3758","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","offset":96,"limit":80},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n96: - Property cards: Photo, price, address, bed/bath, sqft, \"Available Now\" badge, rating stars\n97: - Map/list toggle view\n98: - \"Save\" button per card\n99: \n100: **Detail Page Patterns:**\n101: - Large photo gallery with thumbnail strip\n102: - Floor plan section (image uploads)\n103: - Amenities grid with checkmarks\n104: - Map with nearby points of interest (transit, restaurants, schools)\n105: - Contact sidebar: Phone, Email, Schedule Tour, Apply Online\n106: - Price history and availability timeline\n107: \n108: **Admin/Manager Dashboard (Apartments.com Manager):**\n109: - Property portfolio overview\n110: - Listing performance stats (views, leads, inquiries)\n111: - Lead/inquiry inbox with statuses (New, Contacted, Tour Scheduled)\n112: - Property listing editor (photos, description, pricing, availability)\n113: \n114: ---\n115: \n116: ### Competitor 3: Redfin Rentals (redfin.com/rentals)\n117: \n118: **Type:** Full real estate platform (sales + rentals), Redfin-owned\n119: **USP:** Operated by brokerage; unified renter/buyer/seller dashboard; \"Renter Dashboard\" for saved searches and application tracking\n120: \n121: **Live analysis (2026-05-19):**\n122: \n123: **Universal Gateway Approach:**\n124: - Redfin homepage serves Buy, Rent, Sell, Mortgage, and Agent discovery under one roof\n125: - Primary nav: Buy, Rent, Sell, Mortgage, Real Estate Agents — each with dropdown submenus\n126: - Hero section: \"Redfin Early Access. Find it first.\" with tabbed CTAs (Buy, Mortgage, Sell, Rent)\n127: - Each CTA tab has its own visual, copy, and link\n128: \n129: **Rental-specific Navigation & Pages:**\n130: - Dedicated Rent top-nav dropdown with: Renter dashboard, Rental market tracker, \"How much rent can I afford?\", \"Should I rent or buy?\", Renter guide, \"List my home for rent\", \"Rental Tools dashboard\", \"US rental market trends\"\n131: - User dropdown (signed-in): Feed, Favorites & comments, Saved searches, My homes, Renter dashboard, My Redfin agent, Appointments, Open house schedule\n132: \n133: **Landing Page Sections (redfin.com):**\n134: 1. **Hero + Tabs** — \"Redfin Early Access. Find it first.\" with 4 action cards (Buy, Mortgage, Sell, Rent). Each has icon image + headline + description + CTA button.\n135: 2. **App Download** — Phone mockup + QR code + \"Get the Redfin app\" with brief copy\n136: 3. **Talk to a Redfin Agent** — \"Where are you searching for homes?\" input + assurance (\"no pressure or obligation\")\n137: 4. **Latest Homes Grid** — City name grid cards: \"Browse the newest homes from around the country\" with ~20 city links\n138: 5. **City/State Browse Links** — Alphabetical city links + state links for SEO and discovery\n139: 6. **Footer** — 4-column structure: Join us (Agent, Referrals, Careers), Find homes faster (app badges), About us (Why Redfin, Community, Inclusion, Culture, Blog), Find us (Contact, Help), Subsidiaries (Rent., ApartmentGuide), Affiliated Business (Rocket Close, Rocket Mortgage)\n140: \n141: **Key Insights:**\n142: - Renter Dashboard is a first-class navigation item (not buried)\n143: - Financial tools are deeply integrated (rent affordability calculator, rent vs. buy calculator)\n144: - Strong cross-promotion with Redfin agent network and mortgage services\n145: - Desktop-first with prominent app download CTAs\n146: \n147: **Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n148: - Consider rent affordability calculator as a differentiator\n149: - Make \"Favorites\" a top-level nav item from the start\n150: - Rental-specific content (market trends, renter guides) drives SEO and engagement\n151: \n152: ---\n153: \n154: **Type:** Short-term rental marketplace\n155: **USP:** Best-in-class UX, immersive design, host/guest marketplace\n156: \n157: **Landing Page Patterns:**\n158: - Category bar (horizontal scroll chips): Rooms, Mansions, Amazing pools, Cabins, etc.\n159: - Card grid with large photos, location name, distance, dates, price per night\n160: - Each card: Carousel of photos, heart (wishlist) button, location, host type, rating, price\n161: - Search: \"Where\", \"Check in / Check out\" (date picker), \"Who\" (guests selector)\n162: - \"Inspiration for your next trip\" sections (themed, curated)\n163: \n164: **Detail Page Patterns:**\n165: - Full-width immersive photo gallery with \"Show all photos\" button\n166: - Title, rating, location, host info in header\n167: - Sectioned below: Description, What this place offers (amenities with icons), Where you'll sleep (bedroom breakdown), Map, Host info, Things to know (house rules)\n168: - Right sidebar: Price, date picker, guest selector, \"Reserve\" CTA, total calculation\n169: - Wishlist/save functionality (heart icon)\n170: \n171: **Key Design Lessons:**\n172: - Immersive, photo-first design\n173: - Card carousels on search results pages\n174: - Sectioned, scannable detail pages\n175: - Sticky booking/reserve sidebar (or bottom bar on mobile)\n\n(Showing lines 96-175 of 472. Use offset=176 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"- Property cards: Photo, price, address, bed/bath, sqft, \"Available Now\" badge, rating stars\n- Map/list toggle view\n- \"Save\" button per card\n\n**Detail Page Patterns:**\n- Large photo gallery with thumbnail strip\n- Floor plan section (image uploads)\n- Amenities grid with checkmarks\n- Map with nearby points of interest (transit, restaurants, schools)\n- Contact sidebar: Phone, Email, Schedule Tour, Apply Online\n- Price history and availability timeline\n\n**Admin/Manager Dashboard (Apartments.com Manager):**\n- Property portfolio overview\n- Listing performance stats (views, leads, inquiries)\n- Lead/inquiry inbox with statuses (New, Contacted, Tour Scheduled)\n- Property listing editor (photos, description, pricing, availability)\n\n---\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779182020206,"end":1779182020513}},"id":"prt_e3f831d3c001pP2SchF6TLC4gU","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f830623001XO4JZvExvtuiAU"}}
