{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182045708,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_HGAv0XHstcHIaVnPlMm59672","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","offset":225,"limit":50},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n225: - \"What is Rentable?\" about section\n226: - \"Advertising a Property?\" partner CTA\n227: - Trusted by: Forbes, MarketWatch, CNBC, Realtor.com, Washington Post logos\n228: \n229: **Key Design Lessons:**\n230: - Social proof sections (press mentions, trust logos, ratings)\n231: - City/campus browse grids for SEO and discovery\n232: - Clear value proposition: \"Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\"\n233: - Strong mobile-first design\n234: \n235: ---\n236: \n237: ### Competitor 5: HotPads (hotpads.com)\n238: \n239: **Type:** Map-centric rental search (owned by Zillow Group)\n240: **USP:** Map-first browsing experience with polygon search\n241: \n242: **Landing Page Patterns:**\n243: - Minimal: search + city links\n244: - No landing \"page\" — immediately drops users into map search\n245: \n246: **Search/Listing Page Patterns:**\n247: - Full-screen map as primary interface\n248: - Listing cards overlay on top of map\n249: - Polygon search (draw area on map)\n250: - Filter bar: Price, Beds, Property Type, More\n251: - Color-coded map pins by price tier\n252: - \"My HotPads\" section: Saved searches, saved listings\n253: \n254: **Key Design Lessons:**\n255: - Map as the primary interface (alternative to card-first approach)\n256: - Minimal design with high information density on map\n257: \n258: ---\n259: \n260: ## Reference UI Patterns\n261: \n262: ### Pattern 1: Property Search Card\n263: \n264: **Present in 100% of competitors.** The standard rental property card contains:\n265: \n266: | Element | Typical Size/Position | Prevalence |\n267: |---------|----------------------|------------|\n268: | Primary photo (thumbnail) | Top, ~280-340px width, 16:9 or 4:3 ratio | 100% |\n269: | Price | Large, bold, top-right or bottom-left of photo | 100% |\n270: | Address/Location | Below photo, primary text | 100% |\n271: | Bed/Bath Count | Below photo, secondary text (e.g., \"2 bd | 1 ba\") | 100% |\n272: | Square Footage | Below photo, secondary text | 80% |\n273: | Property Type Badge | On photo overlay (e.g., \"Apartment\", \"Condo\") | 60% |\n274: | Favorite/Heart Toggle | Top-right corner of card or photo | 80% |\n\n(Showing lines 225-274 of 474. Use offset=275 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"- \"What is Rentable?\" about section\n- \"Advertising a Property?\" partner CTA\n- Trusted by: Forbes, MarketWatch, CNBC, Realtor.com, Washington Post logos\n\n**Key Design Lessons:**\n- Social proof sections (press mentions, trust logos, ratings)\n- City/campus browse grids for SEO and discovery\n- Clear value proposition: \"Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\"\n- Strong mobile-first design\n\n---\n\n### Competitor 5: HotPads (hotpads.com)\n\n**Type:** Map-centric rental search (owned by Zillow Group)\n**USP:** Map-first browsing experience with polygon search\n\n**Landing Page Patterns:**\n- Minimal: search + city links\n- No landing \"page\" — immediately drops users into map search","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779182045343,"end":1779182045706}},"id":"prt_e3f837e6e001qvBiyGqUxNhBya","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f8371aa001Bd6YjUZMNtwzPO"}}
