{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182068960,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_2hMBZcFYObR7dDxfuyxA6310","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","limit":15,"offset":196},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n196: 7. **Footer** — 4-column: Our Company (Redfin.com, Blog, Research, Legal), Popular Searches (8 categories), Let Us Help (App, Avoid Scams, List Property, Business Solutions, Rent Estimator, Accessibility), App badges\n197: \n198: **Property Card Pattern (Rent.com):**\n199: - Image: ~400x270px, 3:2 ratio\n200: - Badges on image: \"$55 Price Drop\" (green), \"1 Month Free!\" (blue), \"Popular\" (orange)\n201: - Below image: Price (large, bold), Property name, Address (street + city/state/ZIP), Bed/Bath (e.g., \"1–2 Beds • 1–2 Baths\")\n202: - No heart/favorite icon visible on cards (favoriting may require signed-in state)\n203: \n204: **Key Insight:** Rent.com uses badges aggressively on property cards to highlight deals and urgency — Price Drop, Month Free, and Popular badges create FOMO and scanability.\n205: \n206: **Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n207: - Property card badges (Price Reduced, New Listing, Popular) increase engagement\n208: - Blog/resource section establishes authority and improves SEO\n209: - Browse-by-directory structure (city/state hierarchy) is critical for SEO traffic\n210: \n\n(Showing lines 196-210 of 474. Use offset=211 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"7. **Footer** — 4-column: Our Company (Redfin.com, Blog, Research, Legal), Popular Searches (8 categories), Let Us Help (App, Avoid Scams, List Property, Business Solutions, Rent Estimator, Accessibility), App badges\n\n**Property Card Pattern (Rent.com):**\n- Image: ~400x270px, 3:2 ratio\n- Badges on image: \"$55 Price Drop\" (green), \"1 Month Free!\" (blue), \"Popular\" (orange)\n- Below image: Price (large, bold), Property name, Address (street + city/state/ZIP), Bed/Bath (e.g., \"1–2 Beds • 1–2 Baths\")\n- No heart/favorite icon visible on cards (favoriting may require signed-in state)\n\n**Key Insight:** Rent.com uses badges aggressively on property cards to highlight deals and urgency — Price Drop, Month Free, and Popular badges create FOMO and scanability.\n\n**Design Lessons for NestFind:**\n- Property card badges (Price Reduced, New Listing, Popular) increase engagement\n- Blog/resource section establishes authority and improves SEO\n- Browse-by-directory structure (city/state hierarchy) is critical for SEO traffic\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779182068618,"end":1779182068958}},"id":"prt_e3f83da0a001VOtSi7BdnX1xhW","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f83cc34001boyBMQ6YG5HK8x"}}
