{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182075712,"sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_R8h820K3APY5OmzGWQPS9353","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","limit":30,"offset":211},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n211: ---\n212: \n213: **Type:** Rental marketplace with verified listings focus\n214: **USP:** Human-verified listings, budget calculator, mobile-first\n215: \n216: **Landing Page Patterns:**\n217: - Hero: \"Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\" + city search input\n218: - Listing count prominently displayed: \"Browse 10,377,478 apartments\"\n219: - Grid of popular cities with images\n220: - Grid of \"Apartments for Rent Near College Campuses\"\n221: - Testimonials and press mentions (Curbed, NBC Today)\n222: - Mobile app promotion with ratings (4.7 Apple, 3.6 Google Play)\n223: - Rent affordability calculator CTA\n224: - \"Real Apartments, Verified by Real People\" trust section\n225: - \"What is Rentable?\" about section\n226: - \"Advertising a Property?\" partner CTA\n227: - Trusted by: Forbes, MarketWatch, CNBC, Realtor.com, Washington Post logos\n228: \n229: **Key Design Lessons:**\n230: - Social proof sections (press mentions, trust logos, ratings)\n231: - City/campus browse grids for SEO and discovery\n232: - Clear value proposition: \"Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\"\n233: - Strong mobile-first design\n234: \n235: ---\n236: \n237: ### Competitor 7: HotPads (hotpads.com)\n238: \n239: **Type:** Map-centric rental search (owned by Zillow Group)\n240: **USP:** Map-first browsing experience with polygon search\n\n(Showing lines 211-240 of 474. Use offset=241 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\n\n**Type:** Rental marketplace with verified listings focus\n**USP:** Human-verified listings, budget calculator, mobile-first\n\n**Landing Page Patterns:**\n- Hero: \"Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\" + city search input\n- Listing count prominently displayed: \"Browse 10,377,478 apartments\"\n- Grid of popular cities with images\n- Grid of \"Apartments for Rent Near College Campuses\"\n- Testimonials and press mentions (Curbed, NBC Today)\n- Mobile app promotion with ratings (4.7 Apple, 3.6 Google Play)\n- Rent affordability calculator CTA\n- \"Real Apartments, Verified by Real People\" trust section\n- \"What is Rentable?\" about section\n- \"Advertising a Property?\" partner CTA\n- Trusted by: Forbes, MarketWatch, CNBC, Realtor.com, Washington Post logos\n\n**Key Design Lessons:**\n- Social proof sections (press mentions, trust logos, ratings)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779182075358,"end":1779182075710}},"id":"prt_e3f83f40e001rV3ZoCw8jaTDPF","sessionID":"ses_1c07feae8ffe1KM7G6zC8Y3nGT","messageID":"msg_e3f83e5a9001VGT86DsA1Q8mKO"}}
